{"type": "article", "id": 56306, "title": "这组小巧雅致的胸针，原型是Eames夫妇的经典产品｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-09-11T22:47:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 52675, "name": "ACME Studios"}, {"id": 52676, "name": "WHENWATCH"}, {"id": 52677, "name": "Charles & Ray Eames"}, {"id": 52678, "name": "alejandra perini"}, {"id": 52679, "name": "Todd Oldham"}, {"id": 18827, "name": "Sebastian Bergne"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 90, "image": "img/article/article_show/201809112304313XGn0SbH8lDz4uqI.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s5 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s6 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s7 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s8 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} span.s9 {font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Charles &amp; Ray Eames Pins from ACME Studios</h3><p>Charles &amp; Ray Eames 夫妇的经典设计掳获了大批粉丝，也有无数后来者效仿他们，或者推出致敬其经典设计的作品。不管是 Charles &amp; Ray Eames 夫妇设计作品的粉丝，或者是胸针收藏家，这一组来自 ACME Studios 的 Charles &amp; Ray Eames 别针，会是个不错的购买选择。</p><p>设计师认为，很多人买不起真正的 Eames 椅子或是其他品类的家具，于是他们设计了这些别针，或许是拥有一段经典设计历史的绝佳方式。ACME Studios 提供了三种经典设计：DCW 椅子，House Bird 和 Dots。胸针由锌合金制成，手工制作的掐丝珐琅，并用蝴蝶背衬固定。售价 14 美元，<a href=\"https://acmestudio.com/the-family/shop/Charles-Ray-Eames-504/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230644axpE3Pj1kULsYAZd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.783951\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230645lhr219EbZpDNLMyF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230645SkXUDrLxgohFwMiJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.829630\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230645QFVHEI96Xmf8ZePn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809112306454uk91eMEBW7YXLs6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.829630\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Aura by alejandra perini</h3><p>西班牙设计师 alejandra perini 推出了一款名为 Aura 的花瓶系列。Aura 也可译为女性的名字，这是日常生活中的一种光反射现象，根据一个人的情绪状态的变化，光影的颜色也会发生一系列的变化，Aura 花瓶系列正是利用了这一现象。</p><p>Aura 系列由三个不锈钢瓶状物制成，其中沿着花瓶的可见焊缝赋予了每件作品独特的美。这些焊缝被设计师解释为疤痕或瑕疵，它们在持续的变化中显示着不同的颜色阴影，仿佛讲述着独特的故事。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230721DNaF5bLTBr6J0lXk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612800\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230721kv71GfMiHAwLPeEc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500901\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230722PfUlyT3ZKsw84a9N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612800\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230722xG0nziumIYEeSJC6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230722gVC0PwTcemjy7E89.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230722TH7glR6ac1dbDrYK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://alejandraperini.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Aura</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The home collection by Todd Oldham</h3><p>美国传奇设计师 Todd Oldham 创立的儿童家具品牌 Kid Made Modern，以视觉效果突出的艺术品和工艺品而闻名。其最新推出的 The Home 系列，意在激发孩子们的创造力。</p><p>The Home 家居用品系列，包括床上用品、地毯、地垫等，试图满足每个孩子的个性化需求。丰富多彩的设计和富有表现力的图案出现在整个系列中，床上用品设计包括空间，动物和颜色等主题，适合为孩子庆祝新学年的开始，或是生日。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230814LfrYBqwlj69Mie4S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000781\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230815neOBZHpKYwgta1Gl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809112308174A7QvfrE0qSDXmhC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230817uprtKaAOWGMQZzRl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230817PoDCWpzKh0qk7eZy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230817FlhsGR1wUBVaTSWd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230818DVU15i2tLfg3pdGN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230819qpacbQNwght1uZDx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/kid-made-modern-launches-a-home-collection-for-children/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Ha’ by Sebastian Bergne</h3><p>英国设计师 Sebastian Bergne 和日本陶器公司东京西海合作推出了一个名为 Ha’ 的瓷器品牌。</p><p>他们把现代设计美学和南日本的传统的陶瓷制造工艺结合起来，生产那些可以插配线条凌厉的鲜花和植物的花器。 Ha' 旨在帮助我们更加沉静地生活在一个千变万化的世界。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230918eml9Uc6sYBkh815d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809112309181Ppxw3fhAXZtoqma.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230921zQk9iZ3CYexGWMIq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809112309214jkrKUs5zcEmApvI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230921hT7wbyjLtfJCHKuQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230921bgPNvj20QuDpJLkE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502344\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911230922QUKF217zphHiPLmy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.689844\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://haporcelain.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ha’</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Fold Series by Olivier Grégoire</h3><p>当我们考虑家具设计时，我们并不完全专注于其主要功能——舒适性。相反，我们将目光投向设计细节，比如形式、材料和工艺。工业设计师 Olivier Grégoire 的折叠系列，是个不错的融合例子。</p><p>折叠系列完全由玻璃纤维制成，有原色系，白色以及黑色饰面，它其实就是 Olivier 折叠椅的变体，带一点失重的感觉。</p><p>这个系列最初是为品牌 Acne Studios 创作的限量版，经过几番调整后，如今已能够适应大规模生产。玻璃纤维坚固耐用的特性，亦允许其在室外使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911231020ALv1Uc4adSDP3htR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644375\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809112310202fIuAJr5klXg3oYs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911231021JXNjMQ34lUSWi0sH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911231021ZuBfNEHbPAmUT51q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666364\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911231022GRv7xOf8VSeFJ2Ti.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809112310226jWiOvcVB28auL4z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.331815\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.oliviergregoire.com/Fold-series\" rel=\"nofollow\">Olivier Grégoire</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Kung Fu Time Clock by WHENWATCH</h3><p>时钟品牌 WHENWATCH 推出新品功夫时钟，设计师使用世界知名功夫明星李小龙的经典元素，加上将战斗模式转化为时针与分针，运用巧思向中国武术表示敬意。</p><p>挂钟表盘直径 220 毫米，根据当下时间分针与秒针不同位置，展现功夫战斗姿势。整座挂钟由可回收材料制成，也符合中国功夫自然正气，无欲则刚的精神气质。售价 45 美元，<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/shop/design/kung-fu-time-clock-whenwatch-09-10-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911231220V08ti1uPfyoaKmMF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.744912\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911231138MJPSwr5E0zZI39k4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664393\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911231141uyxOgNS5zQVC0Frm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.839018\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911231141HB27mqD8TL1OvC0P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.838753\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180911231142nOPDqW2GXQIMtRwN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.734332\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}